description: This is a trivia game on how well do you know your sharing economy. Also this is another way for you to earn money in the sharing economy if you haven't participate in one before or haven't heard of the others yet in the sharing economy. Use it to test out your friends or brush up your local and tech knowledge about the sharing economy.
name: Sharing Economy
shortDescription: Survive the Sharing Economy Trivia. How well do you really know your sharing economy? Also find out about ones you haven't tried out yet, too.
